reviewText: this is a awesome movie. as for remakes go this one is pretty good and stays true to the classic film. love the cast especialy jessica biel she did awesome. the acting is good, the story is good and the special effects are good. the guy who played leatherface did awesome. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do
This remake is pretty bad when compared to the original. This really didn't need to be made but since it was I had to add it to the collection it was better than TCM the next generation.
I love this movie a great reboot.
